title: Lexus IS300h F SPORT
description: Taking the bold styling of the IS to the next level, the IS F SPORT boasts exclusive bolstered front sport seats, a perforated leather-trimmed steering wheel and shift knob, aluminum pedals, Silver Performance interior trim, black headliner and stainless-steel front door-sill scuff plates. Outside, you'll find a more aggressive front fascia and grille, front fender badges and F SPORT wheels.
name: Mark Aaltonen

title: BMW M4 Coupé
description: High performance, outstanding technology and the true sensation of motor sports can be expressed in one single letter: M. M Power World offers exclusive information on M high-performance automobiles – and is the place for everyone united by a common passion: the thrill of the strongest letter in the world.
name: John Johnson
